<collectingCountry id="F34D761893708876FE5BFB42FD8AFB00" box="[509,608,1217,1238]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="415">BRAZIL</collectingCountry>
:
</emphasis>
<collectingRegion id="499EF86A93708876FDC8FB42FF06FB27" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="4" pageNumber="415">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
: Cantareira, 
<date id="FFE4104893708876FEDFFB5FFE00FB27" box="[377,490,1244,1265]" pageId="4" pageNumber="415" value="1963-03-01">1-III-1963</date>
. Specimens are deposited in BMNH and WOPC.
</paragraph>
